onut flesh in this recipe. Fresh coconut flesh freezes well and can also be purchased pre-frozen in most Asian stores.","You can store this chutney in the refrigerator for up to 1 week.","Serve as a side to your favourite curry, snack, appetiser or bread. We served ours with Rava idli (please refer to the recipe on this recipe chip)."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","35m","1 total recipe"]}